<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Frog Lily Pad Run</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="game-panel">
      <div class="panel-header">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Arcade Pond</p>
          <h1>Frog Lily Pad Run</h1>
        </div>
        <button id="restartButton" type="button">New Pond</button>
      </div>

      <div class="hud">
        <div class="hud-card">
          <span class="hud-label">Score</span>
          <strong id="scoreValue">0</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-card">
          <span class="hud-label">Pads Left</span>
          <strong id="padsValue">0</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="hud-card hud-card-wide">
          <span class="hud-label">Status</span>
          <strong id="statusValue">Press an arrow key or WASD to start.</strong>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="game-frame">
        <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="860" height="560" aria-label="Frog lily pad game area"></canvas>
        <div class="scanlines" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="info-panel">
      <div class="info-card">
        <h2>How to Play</h2>
        <p>Use the arrow keys or WASD to hop through the pond.</p>
        <p>Green pads can turn yellow, sink, and reappear somewhere else in the pond.</p>
        <p>Red pads are unsafe, so steer around them.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h2>Goal</h2>
        <p>Stay alive as long as possible and keep hopping before the pad beneath the frog disappears.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
